<li><a href="/wiki/Plymouth_Brethren" title="Plymouth Brethren">Plymouth Brethren</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Quakers" title="Quakers">Quaker</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Calvinism" class="mw-redirect" title="Calvinism">Reformed</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/United_and_uniting_churches" title="United and uniting churches">United Protestant</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Waldensians" title="Waldensians">Waldensian</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Nondenominational_Christianity" title="Nondenominational Christianity">Nondenominational Christianity</a></li></ul></li></ul></td>
</tr><tr><th class="sidebar-heading" style="padding-bottom:0;">
<a href="/wiki/Restorationism" title="Restorationism">Restorationist</a></th></tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content hlist" style="padding-top:0;">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Christadelphians" title="Christadelphians">Christadelphians</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Iglesia_ni_Cristo" title="Iglesia ni Cristo">Iglesia ni Cristo</a></li>
